<section class="hero">

<h1>Miniature Connectors (≤ 2.54 mm)</h1>

<p class="justify">

Engineers face significant challenges when selecting connectors for modern electronic systems due to PCB space restrictions and size constraints. Molex miniature connectors uniquely balance mechanical robustness and electrical reliability in compact form factors, enabling reliable performance in HVAC, Consumer, Automotive, Industrial, and Medical applications.

</p>

