<!-- ENGINEERING REFERENCE -->

<section>

<h2>Engineering Reference: How to Select Connector Pitch</h2>

<p class="justify">

Connector pitch selection affects electrical performance, mechanical reliability, and PCB utilization. Smaller pitch connectors enable compact design but require careful current and mechanical considerations.

</p>

</section>


